&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thoughtfully Designed Schedules:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We offer a predictable schedule with a single, direct rate of pay, including:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Part-time roles&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;with flexible 5-, 3- or 2-day-per-week options.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to pick up additional hours on Saturdays &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
